query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(a1 b q1 s t1 tq1 u1) */ select acc.location,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 1 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('analytic-number-theory',
'ap.analysis-of-pdes',
'ca.classical-analysis-and-odes',
'complex-geometry',
'homotopy-theory',
'lie-groups',
'mp.mathematical-physics',
'operational-amplifier',
'performance',
'power-supply',
'real-analysis',
'riemannian-geometry',
'sql-server-2008-r2',
'sql-server-2012',
'transistors')
inner join answer AS a1
on q1.id = a1.question_id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('dba',
'electronics',
'mathoverflow')
inner join badge AS b
on s.site_id = b.site_id AND b.name IN ('Citizen Patrol',
'Commentator',
'Critic',
'Editor',
'Famous Question',
'Informed',
'Nice Answer',
'Notable Question',
'Yearling')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND b.user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 100
inner join account AS acc
on acc.id = u1.account_id group by acc.location order by count(*) desc LIMIT 100;
